  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/3053",
  "title": "fix(release): provide interactive TTY for npm publish",
  "body": "When we enforce 2-factor auth on our accounts, NPM will asks for the OTP\r\nwhich requires an interactive terminal. This is only achievable using\r\nchild_process as per the shellJS FAQ: https://github.com/shelljs/shelljs/wiki/FAQ#running-interactive-programs-with-exec\r\n\r\nThis also reorders the commands so that we can do the rollback without\r\nmaking the code more complex that it is already.\r\n",
